OL,3,CV-levels, GCSE resits, tuition fees:
OL,4,CEducation secretary answers your
OL,5,Cquestions
OL,7,FITV News Digital Political Reporter
OL,8,FLewis Denison sits down with Education
OL,9,FSecretary Bridget Phillipson on her
OL,10,Fplans to reform the education system.
OL,12,FA major overhaul of the education
OL,13,Fsystem is underway, with
OL,14,Fqualifications for over-16s, GCSE
OL,15,Fresits and tuition fees all set to
OL,16,Fchange.
OL,18,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,19,Fsat down with ITV News Digital
OL,20,FPolitical Reporter Lewis Denison to
OL,21,Fdiscuss all the plans.
