OL,3,CV-levels, GCSE resits, tuition fees:
OL,4,CEducation secretary answers your
OL,5,Cquestions
OL,7,FMost significant among the policies is
OL,8,Fthe creation of a new V-level
OL,9,Fqualification which will be available
OL,10,Ffor pupils aged 16 to 19 to study.
OL,12,FThe Department for Education said they
OL,13,Fwill replace level 3 BTEC vocational
OL,14,Fqualifications which are currently
OL,15,Favailable alongside A and T-levels.
OL,17,FIn a blow for those hoping to attend
OL,18,Funiversity, the education secretary
OL,19,Fhas also announced tuition fees will
OL,20,Frise in line with inflation for the
OL,21,Fnext two academic years.
