OL,7,FBut she said Labour would legislate
OL,8,Fwhen parliamentary time allows to
OL,9,Fincrease tuition fee caps
OL,10,Fautomatically in future linked to
OL,11,Fquality.
OL,13,FMaintenance loans will also increase
OL,14,Fin line with forecast inflation every
OL,15,Facademic year.
OL,17,F"We will not allow institutions who
OL,18,Fdon't take quality seriously to make
OL,19,Ftheir students pay more.
