OL,3,CV-levels, GCSE resits, tuition fees:
OL,4,CEducation secretary answers your
OL,5,Cquestions
OL,7,F"Charging full fees will be
OL,8,Fconditional on high quality teaching,
OL,9,Fbalancing stability for universities
OL,10,Fwith fairness for students and for
OL,11,Ftaxpayers," Phillipson said.
OL,13,FDomestic university fees were
OL,14,Fincreased in line with inflation to
OL,15,F#9,535 starting from this academic
OL,16,Fyear after being frozen since 2017.
OL,18,FThe government has also announced new
OL,19,Fcourses which ministers claim will end
OL,20,Fthe cycle of repeated resits for those
OL,21,Fwho don't pass GCSE maths and English.
