OL,7,FDfE said the new qualifications will
OL,8,Fbe "targeted at students with lower
OL,9,Fattainment as a stepping stone to
OL,10,Fbetter prepare them to resit these
OL,11,FGCSEs".
OL,13,FThe current resit rule, which requires
OL,14,Fstudents who do not achieve a grade 4
OL,15,Fin GCSE English and maths to resit
OL,16,Fpost-16, is regularly criticised by
OL,17,Fsector leaders.
