OL,3,CV-levels, GCSE resits, tuition fees:
OL,4,CEducation secretary answers your
OL,5,Cquestions
OL,7,FPhillipson told ITV News that pupils
OL,8,Fmust continue studying maths and
OL,9,FEnglish until they are 18 and resits
OL,10,Fwill still be necessary but the new
OL,11,Fcourses will make students better
OL,12,Fprepared.
OL,14,FThe department added it will
OL,15,Fparticularly "support white working
OL,16,Fclass pupils", with those eligible for
OL,17,Ffree school meals more likely to need
OL,18,Fto resit these exams compared to their
OL,19,Fmore affluent peers.
